NBA Top 10: Lavinovih 360 stepeni [VIDEO]
07 Nov 2019, 12:47 by Nemanja
Atraktivno zakucavanje košarkaša Čikago Bulsa Zeka Levina u duelu protiv Atlanta Hoksa proglašeno je danas za najbolji potez protkele večeri u NBA ligi.
Nekadašnji šampion u zakucavanju je zauzeo dva mesta na ovoj listi, a pored njega tu su još i Janis Adetokumbo (naravno), Dža Morant, Džulijus Rendl…

NBA Top 10: Lavin 360 Degrees [VIDEO]
07 Nov 2019, 12:47 by Nemanja
Chicago Bulls quarterback Zek Levin's attractive knockout performance in the duel against the Atlanta Hawks was announced today as the NBA's best move last night.
The former dunk champion has taken two places on this list, and besides him are Janis Adetokumbo (of course), Ja Morant, Julius Randle…
